{"tid":1618301,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"期待手持午餐肉就可以有西屌嘅日子","createTime":"2019-10-04T05:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T18:15:35.000Z","uid":154406,"like":133,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"31fef442065a9aa8fb3e9b1be47d2e2f1a99dd6e","tid":1618301,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:19:13.000Z","msg":"出解放軍又好,721重演又好,戒嚴宵禁又好,有咩事發生都唔驚,要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然,到有日真係出現全香港範圍MAP炮,就咩都唔使<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VEhyR1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVEhyR1F.jpg&h=eabd2945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放在廚房櫃的鑵頭同米,[現鑵頭總存貨有$10000左右]米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿,到中國午餐肉,回煱肉,豆,菜,金寶湯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YLvpee4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYLvpee4.jpg&h=ee3c88ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一箱箱未開太多,放到出廳[依d全部係魚]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZXGgts.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZXGgts.jpg&h=3d4faedb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n停止供應東江水,未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐,現在D水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n即食麵有5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n另外,打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n全港停擺~~~<br />\n無網上~~無娛樂~~無野買無野食的日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待,手持午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdac34a03bfd3ed75af2f937805711089ae87647","tid":1618301,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:21:17.000Z","msg":"大家儲咗糧未？"},{"pid":"a73f6cb6d5ea61a41dc45cf553c651d5a033c5d1","tid":1618301,"uid":214692,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:22:27.000Z","msg":"想比你屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463a75b7335aa734ab6e2e8c3bb059b4f49e1891","tid":1618301,"uid":154406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid"